"rice paddy](/assets/uploads/876534c6-020f-442c-bb93-833a8f5e5965.jpg)"
msgstr ""
"![A male rice farmer carries harvested rice as he walks alongside a sunny "
"rice paddy](/assets/uploads/876534c6-020f-442c-bb93-833a8f5e5965.jpg)"

